      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh really? i always thought grapefruit was like a superfood and good for heart health. i don't feel any different when i drink it, so is it really that big of a deal? i mean, it's just juice, surely it can't mess with a pill that much? it feels like a bit of an exaggeration.",
