      "content": "i hear people talk about this all the time and it never seems to be a problem for them. like, i've read that the benefits of the vitamins in the juice probably outweigh the risk of a little extra medicine in my system. if i just have a small amount or maybe once or twice a week, is it really going to be unsafe? i'd really rather not change my breakfast routine if it's not actually a major danger.",
