      "content": "Even small or infrequent amounts carry a risk because the interaction can still occur with atorvastatin. Healthcare professionals advise caution because predicting the exact level of drug buildup is difficult to manage without professional guidance. For your safety, it is strongly recommended that you avoid combining grapefruit juice and atorvastatin entirely to prevent potential complications.",
